---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Pricing from '../components/Pricing.astro';
---
<Layout title="Studio — Done-For-You earned media services" description="701am Studio — done-for-you earned-media enrollment fulfillment and organic AI/SEO growth for universities, edtech, and agencies. Inquire for pricing.">
<!-- HERO -->
<header class="ind-hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-atmos"><div class="grid"></div><div class="glow g1"></div><div class="glow g2"></div><div class="glow g3"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ind-eyebrow"><a class="bk" href="/">701am</a> / Studio</div>
    <h1>Done-for-you earned media &amp; <em class="grad">AI visibility</em>.</h1>
    <p class="isub">Run the full earned-media engine without a full-time team. 701am Studio delivers <b>enrollment fulfillment</b> and <b>organic AI/SEO growth</b> for universities, edtech companies, and the agencies that serve them — scoped, staffed, and managed on your behalf.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg js-soon"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio</button>
      <button class="btn btn-soft btn-lg js-soon"><i class="ti ti-player-play"></i>See how it works</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- NAMED PROBLEM -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="problem">
    <div class="problem-eyebrow">The capacity problem</div>
    <h2 class="problem-h">You know the work that needs doing. You just don't have the <em class="grad">team</em> to do it.<br><span class="problem-until">That's what Studio is for.</span></h2>
    <p class="problem-p">701am runs continuously — researching, drafting, monitoring, measuring. Studio puts a dedicated team behind it: we configure the engine to your institution or client, manage the campaigns, and deliver the coverage, rankings, and AI citations that drive enrollment and category authority. You get the output of a full earned-media team without the headcount or retainer overhead.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Studio services</div>
    <h2>Two tracks, one <em class="grad">engine</em>.</h2>
    <p>Pick the track that matches your goal — or run both together.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="landscape">
    <div class="lscard">
      <div class="li" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-news"></i></div>
      <h3>Earned Media Enrollment Fulfillment</h3>
      <p>Full-cycle earned media for enrollment — from data-story research through journalist outreach, placement tracking, and funnel correlation. We find the angles, write the pitches, manage the reporter list, and tie every placement back to inquiry and application movement.</p>
      <span class="lq">Delivered: <b>placements, citations, enrollment signal</b></span>
    </div>
    <div class="lscard">
      <div class="li" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-robot"></i></div>
      <h3>Organic AI/SEO Growth</h3>
      <p>Earn the rankings, outcomes data, and third-party coverage that AI models and search engines prioritize. We build the visibility assets — data studies, category-defining content, press coverage — that compound your institution's presence across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google, and the press simultaneously.</p>
      <span class="lq">Delivered: <b>AI citations, search rank, category authority</b></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Who it's for</div>
    <h2>Built for teams that need <em class="grad">more than software</em>.</h2>
    <p>701am Studio is for institutions and agencies that want the full engine — configured, managed, and staffed.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="forind" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)">
    <a class="ficard" href="/universities">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--gold-soft);color:var(--gold-deep)"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
      <h3>Universities</h3>
      <p>Your enrollment team knows the programs. We run the earned-media engine that makes them the answer in AI, search, and the press — placements tied to funnel movement, not just impressions.</p>
      <span class="more">For enrollment teams <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/edtech">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-device-laptop"></i></div>
      <h3>Edtech &amp; OPMs</h3>
      <p>Your category authority is a competitive advantage. Studio builds the data studies, trade coverage, and AI citations that make you the default choice when institutions evaluate your category.</p>
      <span class="more">For edtech companies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/agencies">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-briefcase"></i></div>
      <h3>Agencies</h3>
      <p>Add an earned-media arm to your agency overnight. Studio runs per-client, isolated, and white-label — you keep the strategy and the relationship, we deliver the placements and visibility data.</p>
      <span class="more">For agencies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY STUDIO -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Why Studio</div>
    <h2>An engine, <em class="grad">staffed</em>.</h2>
    <p>701am is the machine. Studio is the team that runs it — so you get the output without needing to operate it yourself.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="forwho">
    <div class="fw"><i class="ti ti-settings-cog"></i><span class="ft"><b>We configure and manage.</b> Your workspace is set up, your programs and competitors loaded, your voice and guardrails tuned — then the engine runs and we manage the output.</span></div>
    <div class="fw"><i class="ti ti-users"></i><span class="ft"><b>Dedicated campaign team.</b> A real person reviews every pitch, manages every reporter relationship, and ensures every placement ties back to your enrollment or category goals.</span></div>
    <div class="fw"><i class="ti ti-chart-bar"></i><span class="ft"><b>Visibility that compounds.</b> Every ranking earned, every data study published, every placement secured makes the next one easier — your visibility is an asset that builds, not a campaign that resets.</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING -->
<Pricing context="home" />

<!-- CLOSING -->
<section class="closing">
  <div class="catmos"><div class="cg"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pill-badge"><span class="tagm">Filed at sunrise</span></div>
    <h2>Let's talk about what you <em class="grad">need</em>.</h2>
    <p>Tell us about your institution or agency — we'll scope a Studio engagement that matches your goals.</p>
    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg js-soon"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio</button>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
